The vulnerability (CVE-2021-27341) is related to a local file inclusion (LFI) vulnerability in the OpenSIS Community Edition, specifically through the `filename` parameter in `DownloadWindow.php`. This type of vulnerability typically occurs when user input is not properly sanitized, allowing an attacker to include arbitrary files from the server.

### Proposed Modification
The proposed modification is:
```php
